Questions.Question2: How do i create a folder?
Questions.Question3: How do i share files with people?
Questions.Question4: How do i share folders with people?
Questions.Question5: How do i move files to another folder?
Questions.Question6: How do i move folders to another folder?
Questions.Question7: How do i copy files to another folder?
Questions.Question8: How do i copy folders to another folder?
Questions.Question9: How do i rename files and folders?
Questions.Question10: How do i delete files and folders?

Answers.Answer1: Click on the Upload file button and select the file you want to upload. You can upload files in different formats
Answers.Answer2: Click on the New folder button and enter the name of the folder you want to create. You can create folders in different formats
Answers.Answer3: Click on the Share button and select the people and groups you want to share the file with. You can share files with different people and groups
Answers.Answer4: Click on the Share button and select the people and groups you want to share the folder with. You can share folders with different people and groups
Answers.Answer5: Click on the Move button and select the folder you want to move the file to. You can move files to different folders
Answers.Answer6: Click on the Move button and select the folder you want to move the folder to. You can move folders to different folders
Answers.Answer7: Click on the Copy button and select the folder you want to copy the file to. You can copy files to different folders
Answers.Answer8: Click on the Copy button and select the folder you want to copy the folder to. You can copy folders to different folders
Answers.Answer9: Click on the Rename button and enter the new name for the file or folder. You can rename files and folders
Answers.Answer10: Click on the Delete button and confirm the deletion of the file or folder. You can delete files and folders
